### Core Logic

#### [MODIFY] [rewriter.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py)

- Change [_load_prompt(name)](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#106-111) → [_load_prompt(name, lang="en")](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#106-111)
- Logic: try `prompts/{lang}/{name}` first, fallback to `prompts/{name}`
- Pass `lang` parameter through: [analyze_chapter()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#135-185), [rewrite_chapter()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#189-232), [rewrite_chapter_narrative()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#686-766), [verify_chapter()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#226-272)

