### Prompt Content — Español

Key differences from English prompts:

| Aspect | English | Español |
|---|---|---|
| Audience | US, 30+ | Hispanohablante, 25+ |
| Vocabulary | Grade 8-10 | Vocabulario claro, accesible |
| Sentence limit | 25 words | 30 palabras |
| Tone | Calm, subtle | Más expresivo, cálido |
| Output | "In English" | "En español" |
| Cultural refs | US/UK references | España/LATAM references |

